arly to quadratically with the telescope diameter and\nis inversely proportional to the local air speed near the telescope structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2020 13:11:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Dec 2020 09:53:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-04"}
